      "text": "GROUNDEDNESS\nLLM-as-Judge\n\nPrompt: \"Is answer grounded?\"\nOutput: FULL / PARTIAL / NOT\n\nWhy this design:\n• 3-level = catches partial\n  hallucinations\n• \"Made-up specifics = NOT\"\n• \"'I don't know' = GROUNDED\"\n  → honest refusal is good",
